    <thetext>Description of problem:
Based on https://www.freedesktop.org/wiki/Software/systemd/NetworkTarget/ the slapd daemon probably should wait for network-online.target, i.e. the network is up and functional.

Version-Release number of selected component (if applicable):
openldap-2.4.44-1.fc24

How reproducible:
always

Steps to Reproduce:
Not tested, but when IP is obtained from DHCP it may happen that slapd starts before there is network connection.</thetext>
